    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Spanish gold coins issued beginning in the early 16th century; later, these and similar Portuguese coins; and, more recently, various coins of Spanish- and Portuguese- speaking countries.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
